# Portfolio Project — Souala Elhoussine

## Project Overview
A professional portfolio website + backend API for **Souala Elhoussine** — a Full-Stack Engineer, AI Systems Designer, and PhD Candidate in Quantum Computing at USTHB University. The project uses a **Laravel 13 backend** and a **Next.js 16 / React 19 frontend** with Docker containerization.

**GitHub**: https://github.com/Greghori101/portfolio  
**Live**: https://portfolio.level-up-org.com  
**Owner**: Souala Elhoussine — e.souala@esi-sba.dz

---

