## Technology Stack

### Backend (Laravel 13)
| Tech | Version | Purpose |
|------|---------|---------|
| PHP | ^8.3 | Language runtime |
| Laravel Framework | ^13.8 | Full-stack framework |
| FrankenPHP | — | PHP app server (Caddy-based) |
| Vite | — | Asset bundling |
| Pest | ^4.7 | Testing framework |
| Laravel Pail | ^1.2.5 | Real-time log viewer |
| Laravel Pint | ^1.27 | Code formatter |

### Frontend (Next.js 16 + React 19)
| Tech | Version | Purpose |
|------|---------|---------|
| Next.js | 16.1.6 | React framework (App Router) |
| React | 19.2.4 | UI library |
| TypeScript | 5.7.3 | Type safety |
| Tailwind CSS | ^4.2.0 | Utility-first CSS |
| Framer Motion | ^12.34.3 | Animation library |
| Radix UI | Various | Accessible UI primitives |
| shadcn/ui | — | Component system |
| Lucide React | ^0.564.0 | Icon library |
| next-themes | ^0.4.6 | Theme (dark/light mode) |
| Recharts | 2.15.0 | Charts |
| Date-fns | 4.1.0 | Date formatting |
| Zod | ^3.24.1 | Schema validation |
| React Hook Form | ^7.54.1 | Form management |
| Sonner | ^1.7.1 | Toast notifications |
| Embla Carousel | 8.6.0 | Carousel component |

### Infrastructure
| Tech | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| Docker | Containerization (multi-service) |
| Traefik | Reverse proxy + SSL (Let's Encrypt) |
| FrankenPHP | Production PHP server |
| Alpine.js | Backend UI interactivity (Laravel default) |

---

## Architecture

- **Frontend**: Next.js 16 App Router with static/dynamic rendering, hosted in Docker container
- **Backend**: Laravel 13 REST API with FrankenPHP in Docker
- **Networking**: Both containers run behind Traefik reverse proxy on `portfolio.level-up-org.com`
- **Theming**: Client-side dark/light mode via `next-themes` + Tailwind CSS dark variant

## Key Pages / Routes

| Route | Description |
|-------|-------------|
| `/` | Main portfolio page |
| `#about` | About section (scroll) |
| `#experience` | Work experience + tech stack |
| `#projects` | Featured projects |
| `#research` | Academic research & education |

