## Skills / Context Files

- `backend-laravel-13.md` — SOLID principles, Eloquent ORM best practices, API development, testing (Pest), queues, caching, security, performance, deployment
- `frontend-react-19.md` — Component architecture, hooks, state management (React Query/Zustand), Next.js patterns, shadcn/ui, form validation, accessibility, performance
- `souala-elhoussine.md` — Full biography of Souala Elhoussine (education at ESI-SBA, PhD at USTHB, work experience, research interests in quantum computing)